860
00:40:30,530 --> 00:40:31,650
They're back.

861
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:35,270
Why didn't you just break the formation earlier?

862
00:40:36,390 --> 00:40:37,650
I'm tired. I want to take a rest.

863
00:40:37,650 --> 00:40:38,590
Please be quiet now.

864
00:40:39,340 --> 00:40:40,850
The Book of Calming...

865
00:40:41,150 --> 00:40:42,430
Four-digit number...

866
00:40:43,230 --> 00:40:44,350
Linglong House?

867
00:40:53,310 --> 00:40:54,190
What's wrong with her?

868
00:40:55,150 --> 00:40:55,990
Where's Kai Shan?

869
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:58,430
Why haven't you gone to sleep yet?

870
00:40:59,150 --> 00:41:00,870
We're worried about Kai Shan,

871
00:41:01,310 --> 00:41:02,150
so we can't sleep.

872
00:41:02,510 --> 00:41:03,870
What about you? How's it going?

873
00:41:03,870 --> 00:41:04,630
Not bad.

874
00:41:04,990 --> 00:41:06,190
We passed three challenges in a row,

875
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:07,470
and only the final one is left.

876
00:41:26,470 --> 00:41:27,630
It's not here either.

877
00:41:28,550 --> 00:41:29,870
Could it be somewhere else?

878
00:41:34,870 --> 00:41:35,940
What are you looking for?

879
00:41:36,350 --> 00:41:37,310
A book.

880
00:41:37,990 --> 00:41:38,790
Do you need my help?

881
00:41:38,790 --> 00:41:39,550
No, thanks.

882
00:41:47,230 --> 00:41:48,470
That's the situation.

883
00:41:48,870 --> 00:41:49,830
In the final challenge,

884
00:41:49,860 --> 00:41:51,180
if I'm not mistaken,

885
00:41:51,260 --> 00:41:52,860
we have to build a Linglong House.

886
00:41:54,470 --> 00:41:55,040
Interesting.

887
00:41:56,150 --> 00:41:57,710
It really is brilliant.

888
00:41:58,070 --> 00:41:59,100
The Realm of the White Horse,

889
00:41:59,100 --> 00:42:00,060
the Star Map—

890
00:42:00,430 --> 00:42:01,590
each seal

891
00:42:01,590 --> 00:42:02,870
is a profound subject.

892
00:42:02,990 --> 00:42:03,750
And in the end,

893
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:05,430
you even need to build a Linglong House.

894
00:42:06,750 --> 00:42:07,550
My goodness.

895
00:42:07,870 --> 00:42:09,630
This old guy really is something.

896
00:42:10,710 --> 00:42:12,030
Well, if that's the case,

897
00:42:12,150 --> 00:42:13,110
losing to him

898
00:42:13,150 --> 00:42:14,350
wasn't so shameful to me after all.

899
00:42:15,340 --> 00:42:16,220
You don't say.

900
00:42:16,310 --> 00:42:17,870
Kai Shan really knows how to find a good spot.

901
00:42:19,790 --> 00:42:21,630
It's almost dawn. Let's eat something.

902
00:42:21,870 --> 00:42:22,790
I'm hungry too.

903
00:42:25,830 --> 00:42:26,510
Is Ji Tanyin

904
00:42:26,510 --> 00:42:27,590
still looking for something?

905
00:42:28,670 --> 00:42:29,830
She's searched the entire mountain,

906
00:42:29,830 --> 00:42:31,310
not leaving any room unchecked.

907
00:42:31,350 --> 00:42:32,910
Looks like she's searching for a book.

908
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,030
But she didn't answer when I asked her what book she was looking for.

909
00:42:34,470 --> 00:42:35,470
She's gone out now.
